{"tid":1000113,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鐵鎚狂徒闖停車場　連環扑毀19車","createTime":"2019-01-29T08:00:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-29T10:11:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"99af9401d6d90df445a1911d2503bcd09caa867c","tid":1000113,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T08:00:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190129/20601678\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190129%2F20601678&d=2pBoyAcJJfm%2FTk9I6oZxMJwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=10081bd2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190129%2F20601678&h=7e1e554a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190129/20601678</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年01月29日 <br />\n<br />\n鐵鎚狂徒闖停車場　連環扑毀19車<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190129/large/29la6p05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190129%2Flarge%2F29la6p05.jpg&h=19c420ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屯門一露天停車場多輛私家車車窗玻璃被扑爛。張家豪攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】昨晨6時許，58歲姓陳的車場負責人，返回屯門興富街3號的露天停車場，發現有19輛私家車被人用鐵鎚扑爛車窗及倒後鏡刑毀，於是報警；警員接報到場在地上撿獲一柄鐵鎚，警方調查不排除場主因土地糾紛與人結怨而遭報復。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTesla維修逾二萬元<br />\n<br />\n涉事停車場沒有閉路電視，也無保安員，場內泊有保母車、貨車及私家車，被刑毀的私家車包括寶馬、Tesla及Jazz等。Tesla姓杜車主表示，在該處泊車已七至八年，一直相安無事，其座駕三個月前購入，值40多萬元，「冇辦法，呢區車位短缺，有錢都租唔到其他地方，冇理由泊街；屯門區車位月租都貴，成二千幾蚊」，他指今次維修估計逾二萬元，實際還要待維修部報價，「要同場主傾吓，十幾部車被扑」。<br />\n<br />\n另一輛Golf私家車姓黎車主無奈說：「冇試過俾人恐嚇，第一次，唔知咩原因」，他指此車場月租千多元，「香港都唔夠位擺車，呢度成個區唔夠車位，要搵到先再走」，預計要維修數千元。<br />\n<br />\n■記者張家豪  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n私煙佔市場29%　港府稅收損失28億<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n吼準免稅店可記賬　盜卡黨郵輪搵食狂碌400萬珠寶"},{"pid":"c76473efb333c435e46ff1b89201ba6ada406630","tid":1000113,"uid":57462,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T08:01:33.000Z","msg":"以前泊過 夜晚勁黑加冇人<br />\n唔好話扑爛架車 扑條女都冇人知"},{"pid":"27f1a31b5943a2b1d4835e937cadbcdb5833c918","tid":1000113,"uid":60279,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T08:02:43.000Z","msg":"涉事停車場沒有閉路電視，也無保安員<br />\n咁同泊街有咩分別?"},{"pid":"536b8890c3e15aa7057afa51d72b69e3ffb13d78","tid":1000113,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T08:04:26.000Z","msg":"重回70,80年代<br />\n黑社會治港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7b4a3900a79d83af9e911176d10c7f842313778","tid":1000113,"uid":77196,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T08:06:40.000Z","msg":"「<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>香港都唔夠位擺車</strong></span>，呢度成個區唔夠車位，要搵到先再走」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔夠位擺車咪撚買咪得囉，就係呢班仆街搞到日日週街塞車仲要留地起路俾佢地行 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0a68483e412b1a42aed6fd4e77c28ccd3f207bc","tid":1000113,"uid":154702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27f1a31b5943a2b1d4835e937cadbcdb5833c918","tid":1000113,"uid":60279,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T08:02:43.000Z","msg":"涉事停車場沒有閉路電視，也無保安員<br />\n咁同泊街有咩分別?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T08:42:36.000Z","msg":"正想講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ea7d459d01dca5e0c86d94e8ee22212f26fc3d1","tid":1000113,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T08:52:29.000Z","msg":"陰公囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae8885084841193c2dc62cbc66714dd0a537e1e8","tid":1000113,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0a68483e412b1a42aed6fd4e77c28ccd3f207bc","tid":1000113,"uid":154702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27f1a31b5943a2b1d4835e937cadbcdb5833c918","tid":1000113,"uid":60279,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T08:02:43.000Z","msg":"涉事停車場沒有閉路電視，也無保安員<br />\n咁同泊街有咩分別?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T08:42:36.000Z","msg":"正想講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T10:11:23.000Z","msg":"唔驚抄牌"}]}